    <item>
    		<title>UN Security Council removes Indian-flagged oil tanker from blacklist</title>
			<link><![CDATA[http://zeenews.india.com/news/india/un-security-council-removes-indian-flagged-oil-tanker-from-blacklist_1884702.html]]></link>
			<description> The United Nations Security Council on Thursday removed from a UN blacklist an Indian-flagged tanker that was recently prevented from shipping oil for the rival eastern Libyan government after Libya`s UN mission requested the de-listing.
</description>

			<link><![CDATA[http://zeenews.india.com/news/india/up-navnirman-sena-chief-who-threatened-to-kill-jnus-kanhaiya-kumar-arrested_1884656.html]]></link>
